mens.title: D-LAB TAPERED FIT MAN BLUE MEDIUM WASHED JOGGJEANS®

mens.description: Carrot fit with jogger styling for utmost comfort, curved leg narrows to the ankle and has more room on the thigh

mens.title: 2010 STRAIGHT FIT MAN BROWN MEDIUM WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Loose style with a regular waist and straight leg. The silhouette nods to street and hip-hop culture, and features a distinctive label and button fly.

mens.title: D-VIDER TAPERED FIT MAN BLUE MEDIUM WASHED JOGGJEANS®
mens.description: Carrot-leg style with regular waist and pronounced low crotch crafted from JoggJeans® fabric for the utmost comfort. Featuring a dark blue wash enriched with used effects on the waist. Diesel is a proud member of the Better Cotton Initiative. By buying cotton products from Diesel, you are supporting more sustainable cotton production. Better cotton is sourced via a system of Mass Balance and is not physically traceable to end products. See bettercotton.org/massbalance for details.

mens.title: 1979 SLEENKER SKINNY FIT MAN GREY MEDIUM WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Skinny style with a low waist and regular-length, narrow leg from thigh to ankle, designed with a punk-rock attitude in mind.

mens.title: 1995 STRAIGHT FIT MAN BLUE HEAVILY WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Slim style with a regular waist and straight leg. Taking inspiration from the techno music of the mid 90s, this jean features a button fly and an original Diesel attitude.

mens.title: D-PEND STRAIGHT FIT MAN BLUE MEDIUM WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Slim style with a low waist and straight leg. The design is characterised by a cut-off waistband and subtly frayed pockets.

mens.title: 1979 SLEENKER SKINNY FIT MAN BLACK MEDIUM WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Skinny style with a low waist and regular-length, narrow leg from thigh to ankle, designed with a punk-rock attitude in mind.

mens.title: 2021-NC BOOTCUT FIT MAN BLACK CLEAN JEANS
mens.description: Bootcut style with a regular waist and zip fly. The of-the-moment silhouette is trimmed with contemporary detailing and designed for a perfect fit with sneakers.

mens.title: 2019 D-STRUKT SLIM FIT MAN BLACK MEDIUM WASHED JEANS
mens.description: Slim style with a clean construction and essential details. This versatile jean features a comfortable silhouette, finished with a zip fly.

mens.title: 1983 SKINNY FIT MAN BLUE CLEAN JEANS
mens.description: Skinny style with a high waist and regular-length, skinny leg. Finished with a zip fly, this jean fuses a rock attitude with an '80s-inspired look.

mens.title: J-DOIG LOOSE MEN BLACK JACKET
mens.description: Inspired by archival '90s styles, this heavy nylon canvas jacket is defined by piping and a multi-pocket construction. Treated with a water-repellent finish, this men's style is cut to a loose fit with a quilted lining.

mens.title: D-BAS REGULAR MEN BLUE JACKET
mens.description: Men's trucker jacket cut from denim in a vintage medium-blue hue, reinforced with triple stitching.

mens.title: J-WALLY REGULAR MEN BLACK JACKET
mens.description: This men's sports jacket is cut from nylon coated for water resistance. Emblazoned with mega branding on the back, it has a regular fit and a mesh lining. The elasticated cuffs and drawstring hood and hem provide extra protection from wind and rain.

mens.title: D-UM-RIB-NE REGULAR MEN RED SWEATER
mens.description: Men's hoodie in ultra-comfortable Track Denim. Detailed with the oval D logo, it has an oversized fit and ribbed trims.

mens.title: S-UMBE-CHECK-NW REGULAR MEN YELLOW SHIRT
mens.description: Men's regular-fit checked shirt, cut from slub-effect cotton flannel. The collar is embellished with an embroidered D logo.

mens.title: D-SIMPLY REGULAR MEN BLUE SHIRT
mens.description: This men's regular-fit shirt features a clean construction and essential details. Hallmarked with red 'D' embroidery, it's crafted from blue fix denim lasered all-over with a graphic Diesel logo.

mens.title: D-SIMPLY-OVER REGULAR MEN BLUE SHIRT
mens.description: Men's denim shirt with an essential, regular-fit silhouette.

mens.title: D-HOR-FS REGULAR MEN BLACK SHIRT
mens.description: Men's shirt cut for a regular fit from dark-grey fix denim. A unique archival design, it's spliced with contrasting camouflage inserts along the seams and has a vintage logo nestled in the pocket. Subtle treatments confer a naturally worn look.

mens.title: S-CASPER REGULAR MEN GREY SHIRT
mens.description: This men's long-sleeved shirt is cut from viscose satin to a loose fit. Printed all-over with an optical pattern.

mens.title: S-BEN REGULAR FIT MEN WHITE SHIRT
mens.description: Part of the Responsible Collection, this regular-fit shirt is crafted from Italian organic cotton fabric that's compact and has a technical hand feel. Finished with oval D logo embroidery on the chest.

mens.title: T-DIEGOR-E15 SLIM MEN BLACK T-SHIRT
mens.description: Men's fitted T-shirt made from compact cotton jersey. This tee is detailed with contrast stitching along the shoulders and has a zig-zag stitched logo patch on the chest that reads

mens.title: T-JUST-E36 REGULAR MEN BLUE T-SHIRT
mens.description: Men's regular-fit tee made from compact cotton jersey. Branded with a 'Diesel Old Glory' print on the front.

mens.title: T-DIEGOR-E9 SLIM MEN BLUE T-SHIRT
mens.description: Made from cotton jersey and pigment-dyed, this men's T-shirt is flocked on the front with an iridescent 'oval D' emblem. The silhouette is cut slim and has a classic crew neck.

mens.title: T-WASH-E6 LOOSE MEN WHITE T-SHIRT
mens.description: Made from cotton jersey and pigment-dyed, this men's T-shirt is flocked on the front with an iridescent 'oval D' emblem. The silhouette is cut slim and has a classic crew neck.

mens.title: S-SERENDIPITY SPORT MEN BEIGE SNEAKERS
mens.description: Sporty unisex sneakers informed by 2000s styles. Crafted from breathable bicolour mesh, these shoes feature patent and vintage suede overlays, padded D branding and cushioned midsoles.

mens.title: S-ATHENE LOW MAN WHITE SNEAKERS
mens.description: Responsible Collection recycled leather low-top sneakers with pastel-toned suede D patch. Branded with logo eyelets and debossed lettering on the tongue, the upper is set on a speckled rubber cupsole. Triple-stitch detail on the heel tab.

mens.title: D-HAMMER LBT BLACK MAN BOOTS
mens.description: These men's premium black leather boots flaunt an extra-thick rubber outsole and waxed rope laces trekking-style eyelets. Elevated with a stretch collar for comfort and a debossed leather logo tag.

mens.title: S-SERENDIPITY SPORT MULTICOLOR MAN SNEAKERS
mens.description: Men's mesh trainers with rubberised overlays. Branded with a reflective D patch and a moulded rubber logo on the tongue. Set on a cushioned sporty sole.

mens.title: KAUAY SANDALS
mens.description: These flip flops feature slip-resistant soles and textured rubber straps, detailed with a 3D-effect Diesel logo.

mens.title: SERENDIPITY MEN MULTI SNEAKERS
mens.description: Mesh sneakers with vintage suede and soft padded overlays. Branded with a D patch and a heat-pressed Diesel For Successful Living label on the tongue. Set on a cushioned sporty sole

mens.title: S-ATHOS MEN ORANGE SNEAKERS
mens.description: High-top sneakers crafted from washed and dyed denim, set on a thick vulcanised rubber sole with dirty-effect treatment. Reinforced with a rubberised toe cap and contrast outsole, the upper is branded with metal logo eyelets.

mens.title: S-SERENDIPITY SPORT MEN WHITE SNEAKERS
mens.description: Men's running-style sneakers with a 2000s-inspired aesthetic. Set on a chunky cushioning sole, this shoe has a shiny nylon upper overlaid with soft padded panels and suede trims. Complete with contrast stitching, graphic prints and signature D branding on the side.

mens.title: S-RACER LC BLACK MAN SNEAKERS
mens.description: Low-top mesh trainers with hairy suede, smooth leather and grainy leather overlays in an asymmetric design. Featuring an unstitched eyestay and grommet tread, this men's shoe is branded with a layered D logo and an archival tongue patch.
Men's mesh sneakers with off-centre lacing. Multi-textured rubber overlays wrap around the shoe, becoming part of the unique industrial tread pattern.

mens.title: S-RACER LC GREEN MAN SNEAKERS
mens.description: Set on a gripped rubber sole, these men's '70s-inspired sneaker has a nylon and hairy suede upper with an asymmetric toe overlay and unstitched panel edges that reveal pops of contrast. A vibrant appliquéd 'D' emblem accents the side.

mens.title: S-LEROJI MID X MULTICOLOR MAN SNEAKERS
mens.description: These men's high-tops are styled with a leather upper and vulcanised rubber sole, distressed all-over for a lived-in look. Featuring a contrast eyestay with triple-stitch detail, they flaunt a tonal D patch on the side.

mens.title: HIRESH S.II MEN BLUE WALLET
mens.description: Men's bi-fold wallet with a compact design. Made from Italian blue denim, it showcases a lasered monogram motif and classic tobacco stitching. The bright red interior is equipped with various slots and has a pocket for coins.

mens.title: 24 ZIP MEN GREEN WALLET
mens.description: Zip-around wallet in camouflage-print neoprene, finished with drip-proof zips and a bold scratched Diesel logo. The gusseted interior features 8 credit card slots, a zipped coin pocket and various compartments for holding notes, documents or receipts.

mens.title: HIRESH S.II MEN BLACK WALLET
mens.description: This men's bi-fold wallet has a compact design and an internal pocket for coins. It's made from supple nappa leather with an all-over monogram print—the pattern shrinks gradually for a dégradé effect.

mens.title: HIRESH S.II MEN BLUE WALLET
mens.description: Men's bi-fold wallet crafted from denim, featuring a short strap and a coin pocket. The frame-like design is detailed with frayed edges and a leather logo that nods to Diesel's jean branding.

mens.title: B-VISIBLE MEN BLUE BELT
mens.description: Responsible Collection vegetable-tanned leather belt. It fastens with a pin buckle and has a pair of loops—one in leather, the other in metal—that share the Diesel branding.

mens.title: B-MONOGRAM DE MAN BLUE BELT
mens.description: Men's belt crafted from Italian blue denim and red leather, fastened with a metal roller buckle. The denim side showcases a lasered monogram pattern and classic tobacco stitching.

mens.title: B-1DR MEN BROWN BELT
mens.description: This unisex belt is crafted from Italian vegetable-tanned leather and fastened with an antiqued silver 'D' logo buckle.

mens.title: B-GRAIN II MEN GREEN BELT
mens.description: Men's belt crafted from grained leather. The plate buckle is debossed with the Diesel For Successful Living logo and has a slightly aged silver finish.

mens.title: 1DR-POD BACKPACK BLACK BACKPACK
mens.description: Men's ergonomic backpack with a turtle-inspired hard shell construction. Made from durable fabric embossed with a bold 'oval D' emblem, this functional design features contoured shoulder straps, a padded mesh back and a sectioned interior with room for a laptop.

mens.title: TRAP/D BACKPACK MEN SILVER BAG
mens.description: This men's sporty backpack is built from shiny tarpaulin—a durable utilitarian fabric that repels water. Emblazoned with a graphic logo print, it has a matte black base and a roll-top profile with buckles for adjustable volume.

mens.title: DSL UTILITY BACKPACK MEN BROWN BAG
mens.description: nspired by carpenter bags, this men's backpack is fitted with an array of utilitarian pockets in leather, shell and light nylon ripstop. Padded back panel and shoulder straps complement the sturdy, recycled fabric construction.

mens.title: BERLYN BACKPACK MEN BLUE BACKPACK
mens.description: Men's backpack crafted from Italian logo-lasered denim in a stonewashed blue hue. Featuring ergonomic shoulder straps and a zip-around bottom pocket, this jean-inspired design is finished with classic tobacco stitching and rivets on the pull tabs.
